    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo version of Smiths &amp; Legends, you can experience 8 levels from the full game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296470/extras/d6944fedfc52f10b6d57e21a5aa99232.poster.avif?t=1761705632\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296470/extras/d6944fedfc52f10b6d57e21a5aa99232.webm?t=1761705632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296470/extras/d6944fedfc52f10b6d57e21a5aa99232.mp4?t=1761705632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online/Local Co-op</strong> - Play solo or with up to 4 friends in online and split-screen multiplayer.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blacksmithing</strong> - Gather resources to craft weapons, and other goods to sell to customers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat -</strong> Use the items you've crafted to defend your shop from monsters and bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RPG Mechanics </strong>- Carefully manage your Blacksmith’s HP, stamina and weapon durability...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Progression</strong> - Based on your earnings, level up and unlock permanent perks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully voiced storyline - </strong>Will you uncover the secrets of <i>The Legendary Omnismith</i>?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296470/extras/5